      default Advancement save(Consumer<Advancement> consumer, ResourceLocation id, ExistingFileHelper fileHelper)
      save function for the Advancement.Builder which uses the ExistingFileHelper to check if the parent is already known
      Parameters:
      consumer - A Consumer which the build Advancement is passed to
      id - The ResourceLocation for the new Advancement
      fileHelper - The ExistingFileHelper where all known Advancements are registered
      Returns:
      The build Advancement
      Throws:
      IllegalStateException - is thrown if the parent of the Advancement is not known
